<paragraph blockId="6.[112,1317,1207,1945]" pageId="6" pageNumber="285">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[114,267,1881,1906]" pageId="6" pageNumber="285">Bibliography.</emphasis>
Agrawal (2000), Lim &amp; Ross (1992), Molur (2016b), Molur et al. (2005), Musser &amp; Carleton (2005), Smith &amp; Hoffmann (2008).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
